### Nothin API Tests
### Requires VS Code "REST Client" extension
### 
### NOTE: All routes are protected by Clerk authentication.
### To run these tests locally:
### 1. Log in to the app in your browser (localhost:3000)
### 2. Open dev tools, go to Network or Application tab
### 3. Find the Clerk `__session` cookie and paste its value below
### 
@session_cookie = YOUR_CLERK_SESSION_COOKIE_HERE
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@journalId = YOUR_JOURNAL_ID_HERE
@entryId = YOUR_ENTRY_ID_HERE

### 1. Create a new entry (POST /api/entries)
POST {{baseUrl}}/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: __session={{session_cookie}}

{
  "title": "API Test Entry",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "This is a test entry from the HTTP client." }]
      }
    ]
  },
  "mood": "HIGH",
  "tags": ["api", "test"],
  "people": ["Alice", "Bob"],
  "place": "Home Office",
  "journalId": "{{journalId}}",
  "entryDate": "2026-05-27T10:00:00Z",
  "isLocked": false,
  "isPinned": false
}

### 2. Get the created entry (GET /api/entries/:id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/{{entryId}}
Cookie: __session={{session_cookie}}

### 3. Update the entry (PATCH /api/entries/:id)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/entries/{{entryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: __session={{session_cookie}}

{
  "title": "Updated API Test Entry",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "This entry has been updated via PATCH." }]
      }
    ]
  },
  "mood": "VERY_HIGH",
  "tags": ["api", "updated"],
  "people": [],
  "place": "Home Office",
  "journalId": "{{journalId}}",
  "entryDate": "2026-05-27T10:00:00Z",
  "isLocked": true,
  "isPinned": true
}

### 4. Fetch the locked entry (GET /api/entries/:id?unlockCode=123)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/{{entryId}}?unlockCode=123
Cookie: __session={{session_cookie}}

### 5. Soft-delete the entry (DELETE /api/entries/:id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/entries/{{entryId}}
Cookie: __session={{session_cookie}}
